          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1681817099638-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergine is cooking, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) <strong>half</strong> your<strong> ginger</strong> into lengths</p><p>Finely chop (or grate) the <strong>remaining ginger</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>peeled ginger </strong>to a small bowl, cover with<strong> boiled water</strong> and set aside for later – this is your <strong>soaked ginger</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681817103782-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681817103782-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681817103782-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681817103782-x1000.jpg",
