          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1681817103782-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> roughly (if required!)</p><p>Peel and finely chop your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong> then peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Heat a separate pot with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>chopped ginger</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681817108869-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681817108869-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681817108869-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681817108869-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1681817108869-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp] </span><strong>flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [510ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>, <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong>, 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar </strong>and <strong>soy sauce</strong> to the pot</p><p>Cook for 5-6 min or until the sauce has thickened to a curry-like consistency, then blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>– this is your <strong>curry</strong> <strong>sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681817114624-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681817114624-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681817114624-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681817114624-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1681817114624-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain the <strong>soaked ginger</strong>, then add it to a large bowl with your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad,</strong> then pat it dry with kitchen paper, then add to the bowl and give everything a gentle mix up – this is your <strong>quick-pickled ginger salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681817119572-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
