          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681817119572-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681817119572-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1681817119572-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the <strong>curry sauce</strong> to a medium heat to reheat</p><p>Top the <strong>cooked rice</strong> with the <strong>yasai katsu</strong> then spoon over the <strong>curry sauce</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>quick-pickled ginger salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
